{"article_id":"DBGfFVfUQltSCPo4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Attorney Michael Avenatti has for days been claiming","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that he has a client with explosive information about Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and on Wednesday , he and his client finally went public .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"On Twitter , Avenatti posted a sworn affidavit from Washington , DC , resident Julie Swetnick ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"who says","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"she was present at numerous high school parties","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"where Kavanaugh and his friend Mark Judge drank excessively","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"and harassed women .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Swetnick alleges","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that Kavanaugh , Judge , and others targeted women with drugs and alcohol","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"to cause them to \" lose their inhibitions \"","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"so they could be \" gang raped \" -","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"and she says","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"she was a victim of one of these \" train \" rapes .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"( She says","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that Judge and Kavanaugh were \" present \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"when she was raped","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"but does not directly accuse them of participating . )","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"The news adds to the sexual assault and misconduct allegations about Kavanaugh during his younger years ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and comes one day before the first such accuser","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"to come forward ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford , is scheduled to testify before the Senate Judiciary Committee .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Ford alleges","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that at a party in the 1980s ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"while they were all in high school ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Kavanaugh pinned her down ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"tried to take her clothes off ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"and covered her mouth","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"as she screamed","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"as his friend Mark Judge looked on .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Judge ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"whom Swetnick refers to repeatedly in her affidavit as well ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"has declined to testify ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"and committee Republicans have not subpoenaed him .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Kavanaugh has vehemently denied the allegations","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"brought against him by Ford and another woman , Deborah Ramirez ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"who says","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"that Kavanaugh drunkenly exposed himself to her","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and pushed his genitals into her face","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"while they were freshmen at Yale University .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"He has also disputed characterizations","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"of him drinking heavily and partying in his youth ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"despite many of those","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"who knew him","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"saying otherwise .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Judge , now a conservative writer , has written books about his own alcohol abuse while in high school .","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"It ' s not yet clear what Swetnick ' s allegations will mean for Kavanaugh ' s nomination moving forward .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"Republicans have already scheduled a panel vote on his nomination for Friday .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"A spokesperson for the Judiciary Committee said","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"committee lawyers are in the process","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"of reviewing the new allegations .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"The White House released a statement from Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"in which he called Swetnick ' s allegations \" ridiculous \" and \" from the Twilight Zone . \"","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"\" I don ' t know who this is","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"and this never happened , \"","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"President Donald Trump has not yet commented on Swetnick ' s allegations directly","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"but did go after Avenatti on Twitter ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"slamming him as \" a third rate lawyer","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"who is good at making false accusations. \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Avenatti also represents porn actress Stormy Daniels ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"who alleges","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"she had an affair with Trump in 2006 .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Avenatti is a third rate lawyer","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"who is good at making false accusations ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"like he did on me","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"and like he is now doing on Judge Brett Kavanaugh .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"He is just looking for attention","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and doesn ' t want people to look at his past record and relationships","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"- a total low-life !","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"September 26 , 2018","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"According to Swetnick ' s signed declaration ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"she is a graduate of Gaithersburg High School in Gaithersburg , Maryland ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and met Judge and Kavanaugh in 1980 or 1981","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"after being introduced to them at a house party in Washington , DC .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"She says","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"she attended more than 10 house parties with them from 1981 to 1983","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"and observed the pair as \" joined at the hip . \"","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"In the declaration , Swetnick alleges","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"she saw Kavanaugh \" drink excessively at many of these parties","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"and engage in abusive and physically aggressive behavior toward girls , \"","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"including pressing up and grinding against them","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"and trying to shift their clothes","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"to expose parts of their bodies .","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"She says","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"she also saw him be \" verbally abusive \" toward girls","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"and witnessed him act as a \" mean drunk. \"","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"She says","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"other women told her of Kavanaugh ' s behavior in Ocean City , Maryland , during \" beach week , \"","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"which appears on the calendars","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"he has made public .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Swetnick ,","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"who","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"according to the declaration","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"signed it on Tuesday ,","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"says","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"she saw Kavanaugh and his wife Amy ' s interview on Fox News on Monday \" regarding his alleged ' innocence ' during his high school years and lack of sexual activity. \"","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"In the Monday interview , Kavanaugh claimed","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"he was a virgin in high school and for \" many years thereafter . \"","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"\" This claim is absolutely false and a lie , \"","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Swetnick claims ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"she repeatedly saw Kavanaugh \" engage in excessive drinking and inappropriate contact of a sexual nature with women during the early 1980s . \"","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"The most disturbing part of Swetnick ' s allegations regards the \" gang rape \"","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"she alleges","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"occurred at parties","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"where Kavanaugh and Judge were present .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"She alleges","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"that Judge , Kavanaugh , and others would \" ' spike ' the ' punch ' \" at parties","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"\"","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"so as to cause girls to lose their inhibitions and their ability","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"to say ' No. ' \"","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"They would target particular girls ,","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"and","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"if the girls became very drunk or disoriented ,","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"they would be gang raped by a ' train ' of numerous boys . \"","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"She continues :","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"\" I have a firm recollection","depth":16},{"id":121,"text":"of seeing boys","depth":17},{"id":122,"text":"lined up outside rooms at many of those parties","depth":18},{"id":123,"text":"waiting for their ' turn ' with a girl inside the room .","depth":18},{"id":124,"text":"These boys included Mark Judge and Brett Kavanaugh . \"","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"Swetnick says","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"that in 1982 , she was a victim of such a \" train \" rape","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"where Judge and Kavanaugh were \" present , \"","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"but she does not say","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"that they participated .","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"She says","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"she told at least two other people what happened shortly after the incident ,","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"and believes","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"she was drugged","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"using \" Quaaludes or something similar. \"","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"Swetnick says","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"she is aware of other witnesses","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"who can back her up .","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"The declaration also lays out","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"that Swetnick holds a number of federal government clearances ,","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"including from the Treasury Department ,","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"and has held previous federal government clearances in the past ,","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"including from the State and Justice departments .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"Avenatti , a media-savvy figure with 2020 presidential aspirations , has been for days hinting about his client ' s allegations","depth":4},{"id":144,"text":"and making a number of demands of the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":5},{"id":145,"text":"including calling for them to subpoena Judge","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"and to get Kavanaugh to explain","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"what some of his yearbook entries mean .","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"Yet there was skepticism among many","depth":6},{"id":149,"text":"- even top Democrats -","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"about Avenatti ' s claims ,","depth":5},{"id":151,"text":"particularly given how vague they were ,","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"and that they weren ' t being vetted by reporters","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"who were fact-checking them .","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"Now , though , Swetnick has come forward ,","depth":3},{"id":155,"text":"and there will be an effort","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"to evaluate her credibility","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"- which raises the stakes for Kavanaugh ' s appearance Thursday even higher .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":315,"left":300,"right":314,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":204,"right":299,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":192,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":176,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":161,"right":175,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":159,"right":160,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":159,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":2,"ri